<h1>View Project</h1>

<!-- Part 3: View a single project -->
<h4>title: {{title}}</h4>
<h4>goal: {{goal}}</h4>
<h4>description: {{description}}</h4>
<h4>start: {{start}}</h4>
<h4>end: {{end}}</h4>

<h4>Total Amount of Contributions: {{contributionAmt}}</h4>

<!-- Part 4: Contribute to a project -->
